snippet.title: Amber Heard : Elon Musk and James Franco
snippet.description:
can you tell a lot about a person by the company they keep?

Rachael and Kevin discuss the latest developments in the lives of Amber Heard, Elon Musk and James Franco and also possible developments in the Johnny Depp versus Rocky Brooks case.
